OL,3,CFrench lifeguard and council guilty
OL,4,Cover girl's death on school trip
OL,6,FA French lifeguard and local authority
OL,7,Fhave been found guilty of the
OL,8,Fmanslaughter of a British girl who
OL,9,Fdrowned on a school trip.
OL,11,FTwelve-year-old Jessica Lawson, from
OL,12,FEast Yorkshire, died when a plastic
OL,13,Fpontoon overturned in a lake near
OL,14,FLimoges during a trip with Wolfreton
OL,15,FSchool in July 2015.
OL,17,FIn October 2022, three of her teachers
OL,18,Fwere acquitted of manslaughter by
OL,19,Fgross negligence.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/8
