OL,4,Cover girl's death on school trip
OL,6,FAt the time lifeguard Leo Lemaire ,
OL,7,Fwho was on duty at the time of the
OL,8,Faccident, was also cleared, along with
OL,9,Fthe local authority for the town of
OL,10,FLiginiac.
OL,12,FIt left Jessica's parents devastated
OL,13,Fthat no one had been held responsible
OL,14,Ffor their daughter's death.
OL,16,FBut on Wednesday, an appeal court
OL,17,Ffound Lemaire, 30, guilty of
OL,18,Fmanslaughter, along with Liginiac Town
OL,19,FHall.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
