OL,3,CFrench lifeguard and council guilty
OL,4,Cover girl's death on school trip
OL,6,FThe charge stated that there was "a
OL,7,Fclearly deliberate violation of an
OL,8,Fobligation of providing safety or
OL,9,Fprudence".
OL,11,FLemaire was given an eight-month
OL,12,Fsuspended prison sentence. The council
OL,13,Fwas fined 20,000 euros, the equivalent
OL,14,Fof just under #17,000.
OL,16,FBoth parties were ordered to jointly
OL,17,Fpay damages to Jessica's parents, Tony
OL,18,Fand Brenda Lawson, who now live in
OL,19,FPortugal.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/8
