OL,6,FThe amounts were 40,000 euros
OL,7,F(#33,000) for "moral damage", 15,000
OL,8,Feuros (#12,000) for anxiety, and the
OL,9,Fsame amount for the suffering the
OL,10,Ffamily endured.
OL,12,FAll the teachers, Steven Layne,
OL,13,FChantelle Lewis and Daisy Stathers,
OL,14,Fwho were in charge of the group of
OL,15,Fswimmers, were once again acquitted.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/8
