OL,4,Cover girl's death on school trip
OL,6,FThe family has not commented on the
OL,7,Fjudgement, but their lawyer Eloi Chan
OL,8,Ftold ITV News: "The Lawson family is
OL,9,Frelieved with this judgement because
OL,10,Fsomeone has been held accountable for
OL,11,Ftheir daughter's death. I think they
OL,12,Fwere relieved after nearly ten years
OL,13,Fthat the lifeguard and the township
OL,14,Fhave been held accountable.
OL,16,F"It has been a very difficult and
OL,17,Fprotracted struggle for justice...
OL,18,Fthey were yearning for it to come to
OL,19,Fan end because it has been a very
OL,20,Fgruelling process and it has
OL,21,Fintermingled with the process of grief.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/8
