OL,6,FLemaire insisted that he was used to
OL,7,Fseeing the orange pontoon overturn,
OL,8,Fand it was not considered dangerous.
OL,10,FAfter he was acquitted following the
OL,11,Foriginal trial, he said: "Today was
OL,12,Fthe moment the day for everyone to
OL,13,Fmove on and try to move forward with
OL,14,Ftheir lives."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/8
