OL,6,FBut appeal court judges criticised
OL,7,FLemaire - who had denied any
OL,8,Fwrongdoing - for his "lack of
OL,9,Fvigilance" on the day of the tragedy.
OL,10,FThey said the local council was
OL,11,Fparticularly negligent in not putting
OL,12,Fup warning signs.
